#: of numpy.random.RandomState.logseries:51
msgid ""
"The log series distribution is frequently used to represent species richness "
"and occurrence, first proposed by Fisher, Corbet, and Williams in 1943 [2].  "
"It may also be used to model the numbers of occupants seen in cars [3]."
msgstr ""

